'''路易斯安那巴頓魯治聖殿'''（Baton Rouge Louisiana Temple）是[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]的第94座聖殿。1841年，第一次有傳教士到達[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]。現在在路易斯安那中有超過24,000人耶穌基督後期聖徒教會信徒。1998年，教會宣布將興建路易斯安那巴頓魯治聖殿<ref>{{citation |url= http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/30677/5-new-temples-in-US-Mexico-announced.html |title= 5 new temples in U.S., Mexico announced |date= Oct 24, 1998 |newspaper= [[Church_News|Church News]] |access-date= 2016-04-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051350/http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/30677/5-new-temples-in-US-Mexico-announced.html |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>，並在1999年動工 <ref>{{citation |url= http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/35773/2000-attend-ceremony-for-Louisianas-first-temple.html |title= 2,000 attend ceremony for Louisiana's first temple |first1= Karen |last1= Strawn |first2= Gayle |last2= Smith |date= May 15, 1999 |newspaper= Church News |access-date= 2016-04-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304031604/http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/35773/2000-attend-ceremony-for-Louisianas-first-temple.html |archive-date= 2016-03-04 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>，2000年奉獻<ref>{{citation |url= http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/38185/Baton-Rouge-Louisiana-Prosper-the-cause-of-righteousness.html |title= Baton Rouge Louisiana: 'Prosper the cause of righteousness' |date= July 22, 2000 |newspaper= Church News |access-date= 2016-04-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151021232548/http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/38185/Baton-Rouge-Louisiana-Prosper-the-cause-of-righteousness.html |archive-date= 2015-10-21 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

